long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
With FB Reaction Exporter, analyzing your post engagement just got easier. 

This tool is essential for businesses, organizations, and individuals looking to track and analyze engagement on their Facebook posts.

Whether you're a data analyst, business owner, or just interested in personal social media insights, FB Reaction Exporter offers an efficient way to understand audience reactions and refine your social media strategy.

# Features
✓ Download Reactions such as like, love, wow, happy, etc.
✓ Copy to Clipboard (Paste to Google Sheet) 
✓ Analyze engagement on posts and videos
✓ Export data as Excel, CSV, and JSON

# Supported fields:
- User Id
- Username
- Reaction Type
- Avatar URL
- Friendship Status
- Subscribe Status
- Mutual Friends Number 
- Profile URL 
- etc.

# How to get started?
1. Access the Facebook post or video.
2. Click on the FB Reaction Exporter icon.
3. Choose the reactions you wish to download.
4. Click 'Export'.

If it keeps failing, please send us the corresponding link, and we will do some troubleshooting and compatibility.

# Additional Features
- Video Tutorial: Learn how to use this extension with our handy video guide.
- Pro Version: For subscribing to or accessing premium features.
- Feedback: Your feedback matters! If you have any suggestions or issues, reach out to us at support@convlead.com. We are committed to improving your experience.

# Data Privacy
Your data's security is our top priority. Rest assured, all data remains on your device, ensuring 100% privacy and trustworthiness.

# About Pro
FB Reaction Exporter is a paid extension, you can get basic functionality and upgrade to get more functionality.
